public abstract class AbstractProgramData<T extends AbstractProgramData<?>>
extends AbstractAdminData<T>

The class is used to define all program objects used to create / update and to export.

append4Create

protected void append4Create(StringBuilder _cmd)
                      throws matrix.util.MatrixException
Appends the program related MQL commands to create this program. This includes:
  • user
  • hidden flag
  • deferred
  • needs business object
  • downloadable flag
  • pipe flag
  • pooled flag

checkExport

public void checkExport(ExportParser _exportParser)
                 throws matrix.util.MatrixException
Checks the export of this data piece if all values are correct defined. Because the handling of a program is different (the TCL update code is embedded), the values must be checked directly via MQL commands.

Overrides:
checkExport in class AbstractAdminData<T extends AbstractProgramData<?>>
Parameters:
_exportParser - parsed export
Throws:
matrix.util.MatrixException - if check failed
